==Awards and decorations==
* [[Aviator badge]]
* [[Iron Cross]] (1939)
** 2nd Class (4 July 1941)<ref name="Schumann pii">Schumann 2014, p. ii.</ref>
** 1st Class (15 April 1942)<ref name="Schumann pii"/>
* [[Ehrenpokal der Luftwaffe]] on 9 August 1943 as ''[[Unteroffizier]]'' and pilot<ref>Patzwall 2008, p. 79.</ref>
* [[Front Flying Clasp of the Luftwaffe]]
** in Silver (18 June 1942)<ref name="Schumann pii"/>
** in Gold (14 January 1944)<ref name="Schumann pii"/>
* [[German Cross]] in Gold on 17 October 1943 as ''[[Unteroffizier]]'' in the 2./Nachtjagdgeschwader 3<ref>Patzwall & Scherzer 2001, p. 119.</ref>
* [[Knight's Cross of the Iron Cross with Oak Leaves]]
** Knight's Cross on 6 April 1944 as ''[[Feldwebel]]'' and pilot in the 2./Nachtjagdgeschwader 3<ref name="Scherzer p315">Scherzer 2007, p. 315.</ref><ref>Fellgiebel 2000, p. 184.</ref><ref>Von Seemen 1976, p. 130.</ref>
** 531st Oak Leaves on 20 July 1944 as ''[[Oberfeldwebel]]'' and pilot in the 2./Nachtjagdgeschwader 3<ref name="Scherzer p315"/><ref>Fellgiebel 2000, p. 85.</ref><ref>Von Seemen 1976, p. 47.</ref>

